## User Story

As a **user**, I want **faster search results**, so that I can find items more quickly.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: The search results should be displayed within 2 seconds.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: The back-end should be optimized for quicker data retrieval.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Optimize the search query on the back-end.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Implement caching for frequently searched terms.
- [ ] **Task 3**: Test the speed of the search results.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: High
- **Related Issues**: #108
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Consider using an index on the database for faster search performance.
